channel.description:
Noted Ohio Survivalist and Avid Outdoor Enthusiast Tom Lupshu shares information about Earth Changes, Earthquakes, Volcanism, and Natural Disasters of all kinds in this Video Blog. 

sur·viv·al·ist: Someone who tries to insure their personal survival or the survival of their group or nation.

sur·viv·al·ist: One who has personal or group survival as a primary goal in the face of difficulty, opposition, and especially the threat of natural catastrophe, nuclear war, or societal collapse.

sur·viv·al·ist: a person who makes preparations to survive a widespread catastrophe, as an atomic war or anarchy, especially by storing food and weapons in a safe place.

sur·viv·al·ist: a person who advocates or practices survivalism; especially: one who has prepared to survive in the anarchy of an anticipated breakdown of society.
